      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        151.7,
        125.97,
        163.22
      ],
      "text": "Aanleiding",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        171.26,
        506.1,
        182.78
      ],
      "text": "De (ex-)werknemer van de ERD heeft bij UWV melding gemaakt dat de ERD weigert de",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        190.7,
        495.44,
        202.22
      ],
      "text": "behandeling uit te voeren. Deze melding kan door de (ex-)werknemer via het KCC of",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        210.26,
        495.87,
        221.78
      ],
      "text": "schriftelijk zijn gedaan. De melding (verzoek om overname) kan ook van de afdeling",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        229.7,
        429.86,
        241.22
      ],
      "text": "Bezwaar en Beroep, Rechtsbijstand of van de failliete werkgever of zijn",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        249.26,
        228.48,
        260.78
      ],
      "text": "administratiekantoor afkomen.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        85.82,
        268.73,
        515.07,
        280.25
      ],
      "text": "Let op: BO Zwolle en BO Hengelo handelen onderstaand proces af. Komt de melding",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        85.82,
        288.29,
        518.38,
        299.81
      ],
      "text": "binnen op een andere BO? Dan moet de manager Uitkeren het geval eerst overdragen",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        85.82,
        307.73,
        222.62,
        319.25
      ],
      "text": "aan 1 van deze 2 kantoren.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        327.29,
        94.04,
        338.81
      ],
      "text": "Doel",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        346.73,
        522.53,
        358.25
      ],
      "text": "Bepalen of UWV het ziektegeval moet overnemen en zo ja, in UZS de juiste indicatie laten",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        366.29,
        291.56,
        377.81
      ],
      "text": "zetten zodat het geval overgenomen wordt.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        385.73,
        135.14,
        397.25
      ],
      "text": "Functionaris",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        405.29,
        88.89,
        416.81
      ],
      "text": "UD.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        444.29,
        119.51,
        455.81
      ],
      "text": "Gevolgen",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        463.75,
        512.13,
        475.27
      ],
      "text": "Er is beoordeeld of UWV het ziektegeval moet overnemen. Zo ja, dan is in UZS de juiste",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        483.31,
        202.28,
        494.83
      ],
      "text": "overname-indicatie gezet.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        522.31,
        120.34,
        533.83
      ],
      "text": "Instructie",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        78.74,
        542.59,
        497.68,
        554.11
      ],
      "text": "1. Beoordeel aan de hand van de beschikbare gegevens wat de situatie van het",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        562.03,
        238.55,
        573.55
      ],
      "text": "verzoek van overname is:",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        581.59,
        510.32,
        593.11
      ],
      "text": "De ERD heeft de ziekmelding niet in behandeling genomen: ga verder",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        142.58,
        582.42,
        147.16,
        592.38
      ],
      "text": "•",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        601.03,
        218.2,
        612.55
      ],
      "text": "met stap 2.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        634.99,
        507.0,
        646.51
      ],
      "text": "De ERD is gestopt met de afhandeling van de ziekmelding: ga verder",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        142.58,
        635.82,
        147.16,
        645.78
      ],
      "text": "•",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        654.46,
        224.47,
        665.98
      ],
      "text": "met stap 2a.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        688.42,
        511.41,
        699.94
      ],
      "text": "De ERD-werkgever is failliet of via de BOB is een uitspraak ontvangen",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        142.58,
        689.25,
        147.16,
        699.21
      ],
      "text": "•",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        707.86,
        358.92,
        719.38
      ],
      "text": "dat er geen verhaal is. Ga naar stap 9a.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        78.74,
        728.14,
        411.02,
        739.66
      ],
      "text": "2. De ERD heeft de ziekmelding niet in behandeling genomen",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        79.56,
        474.71,
        91.08
      ],
      "text": "Je hebt een verzoek of ziekmelding van de cliënt ontvangen en daarin is",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        99.14,
        473.43,
        110.66
      ],
      "text": "vermeld dat de werkgever de ziekmelding niet in behandeling neemt. Je",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        118.58,
        508.41,
        130.1
      ],
      "text": "controleert eerst of de wettelijke periode van 6 weken is verstreken. Pas als de",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        138.14,
        462.37,
        149.66
      ],
      "text": "wettelijke termijn van 6 weken is verstreken, kan UWV het traject voor",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        157.58,
        479.2,
        169.1
      ],
      "text": "(eventuele) overname van de gevalsbehandeling overnemen van de ERD-",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        177.14,
        165.0,
        188.66
      ],
      "text": "werkgever:",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        196.58,
        327.92,
        208.1
      ],
      "text": "De termijn is nog niet verstreken.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        142.58,
        197.41,
        147.16,
        207.37
      ],
      "text": "•",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        216.14,
        472.69,
        227.66
      ],
      "text": "Verstuur brief SET10I750 ‘Niet in behandeling nemen verzoek",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        235.58,
        491.27,
        247.1
      ],
      "text": "overname’. De cliënt wordt met deze brief geïnformeerd dat UWV",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        255.14,
        474.68,
        266.66
      ],
      "text": "‘nog’ niets doet en op welke datum de cliënt zich opnieuw kan",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        274.61,
        286.24,
        286.13
      ],
      "text": "melden. Einde instructie.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        308.57,
        463.05,
        320.09
      ],
      "text": "De termijn is wel verstreken. Je hebt (opnieuw) een verzoek",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        142.58,
        309.4,
        147.16,
        319.36
      ],
      "text": "•",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        328.01,
        284.59,
        339.53
      ],
      "text": "ontvangen van de cliënt.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        347.57,
        383.26,
        359.09
      ],
      "text": "Je gaat verder met onderstaande instructie.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        367.01,
        516.52,
        378.53
      ],
      "text": "De ERD-werkgever wordt alsnog in de gelegenheid gesteld om de ziekmelding in",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        386.57,
        471.54,
        398.09
      ],
      "text": "behandeling te nemen en te betalen. Daarvoor verstuur je de brievenset",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        406.01,
        516.42,
        417.53
      ],
      "text": "SET11A007 ‘Verzoek om ziekmelding in behandeling te nemen (ERD)’ naar hem.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        425.57,
        219.01,
        437.09
      ],
      "text": "Ga verder met stap 3.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        78.74,
        445.73,
        406.46,
        457.25
      ],
      "text": "2a. De ERD is gestopt met de afhandeling van de ziekmelding",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        465.31,
        505.25,
        476.83
      ],
      "text": "De ERD wordt alsnog in de gelegenheid gesteld om de betaling te hervatten of",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        484.75,
        495.44,
        496.27
      ],
      "text": "een hersteldmelding te doen. Open het scherm Correspondentie bij geval en",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        504.31,
        502.31,
        515.83
      ],
      "text": "verstuur de brievenset SET17G021 ‘Beëindiging betaling door ERD’. Ga verder",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        523.75,
        167.2,
        535.27
      ],
      "text": "met stap 3.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        78.74,
        544.03,
        358.72,
        555.55
      ],
      "text": "3. Voorlegger van het type ‘Herinnering’ aanmaken",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        563.59,
        467.18,
        575.11
      ],
      "text": "Maak via het scherm Beheren voorleggers een voorlegger van het type",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        583.03,
        498.19,
        594.55
      ],
      "text": "’Herinnering’ voor jezelf aan volgens de werkinstructie van signaal UZW0147",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        602.59,
        482.48,
        614.11
      ],
      "text": "Voorlegger. De voorlegger herinnert je eraan om 10 kalenderdagen na het",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        622.03,
        475.8,
        633.55
      ],
      "text": "versturen van de brief te controleren of de ERD de ziekmelding alsnog in",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        641.59,
        499.94,
        653.11
      ],
      "text": "behandeling heeft genomen/de betaling hervat heeft. Als dit niet het geval is,",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        661.06,
        510.02,
        672.58
      ],
      "text": "heeft de (ex-)werknemer dit na de termijn van 6 weken inmiddels aan ons laten",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        680.62,
        143.56,
        692.14
      ],
      "text": "weten.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        700.06,
        511.53,
        711.58
      ],
      "text": "De ERD heeft vanwege de brief alsnog de ziekmelding in behandeling",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        142.58,
        700.89,
        147.16,
        710.85
      ],
      "text": "•",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        719.62,
        512.03,
        731.14
      ],
      "text": "genomen of de afhandeling van de ziekmelding hervat: ga verder met",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 2,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        739.06,
        195.4,
        750.58
      ],
      "text": "stap 4.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        79.56,
        490.18,
        91.08
      ],
      "text": "De ERD heeft vanwege de brief nog steeds de ziekmelding niet in",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        142.58,
        80.39,
        147.16,
        90.35
      ],
      "text": "•",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        99.14,
        387.62,
        110.66
      ],
      "text": "behandeling genomen: ga verder met stap 5.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        132.98,
        491.6,
        144.5
      ],
      "text": "De ERD heeft vanwege de brief nog steeds de afhandeling van de",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        142.58,
        133.81,
        147.16,
        143.77
      ],
      "text": "•",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        160.58,
        152.54,
        392.61,
        164.06
      ],
      "text": "ziekmelding niet hervat: ga verder met stap 7.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        78.74,
        172.7,
        465.96,
        184.22
      ],
      "text": "4. De ERD heeft vanwege de brief alsnog de ziekmelding in behandeling",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        192.26,
        207.06,
        203.78
      ],
      "text": "genomen of hervat",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 3,
      "bbox": [
        109.58,
        211.7,
        478.15,
        223.22
      ],
